## Evidence interpretation

The bridge closes the narrow "bounded target trigger execution" gap for this
diagnostic path: a fresh target trigger produced visible Maya output and trigger
completion inside the watchdog window.

The broader objective is not fully complete yet:

- this is a workspace bridge, not a native Pentagon app poller fix;
- continuous autonomous operation still needs this bridge to be run as a daemon
  or replaced by a native trigger poller repair;
- easy/medium/hard/extra-hard closure still needs a fresh audit proving the
  bridge covers all required task classes without manual intervention.
